{"tid":2087492,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"樂觀d 諗 都係因為港共無我地符先有國安法姐","createTime":"2020-06-30T16:49:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T17:05:10.000Z","uid":32906,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"203a68110edd6ae3b487d49910335c47457786fa","tid":2087492,"uid":32906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T16:49:04.000Z","msg":"證明我地本身潛在有好大可能性<br />\n聽日見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40e6ab1ac9042c16521beb04d968e66ea15a4539","tid":2087492,"uid":266503,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T16:49:29.000Z","msg":"「人民不應該害怕他們的政府，政府應該害怕它的人民。」（People should not be afraid of their governments. Governments should be afraid of their people.）<br />\n<br />\n「藝術家用謊言揭露真相，政治家用謊言掩蓋真相。」（Artists use lies to tell the truth, while politicians use them to cover the truth up.）<br />\n<br />\n「沒有舞蹈的革命，是不值得發動的革命。」（A revolution without dancing is a revolution not worth having）<br />\n<br />\n「面具之下只是個血肉之軀，而在這面具之下的，還有一個理念，只不過，理念，是刀槍不入的。」（Beneath this mask there is more than flesh. Beneath this mask there is an idea, Mr.Creedy, and ideas are bulletproof..）<br />\n<br />\n「我們的尊嚴可能不值錢，但它卻是我們唯一真正擁有的東西。它是我們最後一寸領地，但在那一寸領地裡，我們是自由的。」（Our integrity sells for so little, but it is all we really have. It is the very last inch of us, but within that inch, we are free）<br />\n<br />\n「力量來自團結，團結來自信念」（Strength through unity, unity through faith）<br />\n<br />\n「恐懼往往是政府的終極武器。」（Fear became the ultimate tool of this government）<br />\n<br />\n「就算政府擁有的武力統治不讓人民發言，自由的言論仍然充滿著強大的力量。」（the truncheon may be used in lieu of conversation, words will always retain their power)"},{"pid":"70af042543cab6ebccd487123e4fd7c8dd87a468","tid":2087492,"uid":259402,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T16:50:04.000Z","msg":"中共行完呢條法<br />\n<br />\n仲有冇底牌?"},{"pid":"7b0f80dcaa8a5bf0154ec0f85c21de0bc0a081b6","tid":2087492,"uid":112581,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"70af042543